Why Us?
The folks here at X are passionate about WordPress and pushing it to the limits both in terms of functionality and design. While we like to be on the cutting edge, we believe there is a difference between trend and innovation and that it’s our job to figure out which is which.
Instead of creating just another WordPress Theme, we set out to do something different, and we think you’ll agree that we did just that. Allow us to introduce you to X premium WordPress theme. Get your copy today!

About Us
We Are An Upscale Art Bar & Martini Lounge With Weekly Live Entertainment , Featuring The Very Best Motown, Funk , Soul, Blues And Reggae Bands In Southwest Florida.
We also Cater To Private Parties , Birthday Parties And Corporate Events.
We Take Care Of Everything From Your Customized Food Menu To The Last Adult Beverage Poured.
To Ensure Your Party Or Event Is Nothing Short Of Exceptional!
Private parties and events:
All Reserved Party/Events Of 5 people or more will require a $100 non-refundable reservation fee to reserve specified areas. Reservation fees are refundable if reservations are cancelled within 48 hours of party/event. ( Extra tables for food , desserts etc, as well as table covers and napkins to be provided complimentary upon request)
